{"tid":2242785,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"菲律賓正組建海上民兵派往南中國海 以應對西菲律賓海上的中國海上民兵","createTime":"2020-10-14T09:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T09:25:03.000Z","uid":204533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9b8b8dc33f1e606561542eb0b53e562fc19690","tid":2242785,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:09:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>菲律賓海軍指揮官說，菲律賓將有自己的海上民兵，以應對中國派海上民兵到西菲律賓海騷擾菲律賓漁民。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓海軍司令巴科多中將（VADM Giovanni Bacordo）星期一（2020年10月12日）在參議院作證時說：&ldquo;這是我們與中國海上民兵對應的人員。&rdquo;他說，菲律賓海軍計劃將這些攜帶武器的民兵派往西菲律賓海，到那裡收集數據，並為在那裡捕魚的菲律賓漁民提供保護。<br />\n......<br />\n中國在強化控制南中國海的行動中常常使用半軍事化和非軍事化的手段，其中包括用大量漁民和漁船建立了一個海上民兵網絡。這支龐大的準軍事力量被用來與海軍一起，推進北京的南中國海的戰略。<br />\n<br />\n這些中國漁船常常在有爭議海域騷擾甚至攻擊菲律賓和越南漁船。<br />\n<br />\n2019年6月，一艘中國漁船在斯普拉特利群島(中國稱南沙群島)的里德淺灘(中國稱禮樂灘)附近撞擊了一艘菲律賓漁船。菲律賓媒體報導說，22名菲律賓船員落入海中，被附近的一艘越南船幫助救起，但中國船隻沒有施救便離開事發現場。<br />\n<br />\n前中國海軍司令部中校軍官姚誠2019年5月在美國之音電視節目中說，中國的海上民兵是人民戰爭理念的延續，是武裝部隊的一部分，並與海軍艦隊保持密切聯繫。</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/philippine-maritime-militia-china-scs-20201014/5620842.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fphilippine-maritime-militia-china-scs-20201014%2F5620842.html&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2gx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=566f38c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/philippine-maritime-militia-china-scs-20201014/5620842.html</a>"},{"pid":"e82ce86653e93856bf0fabf04f9b24656b16acb4","tid":2242785,"uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/D3170866-C664-4A42-A91D-49C9AF35AFCB_w1023_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2FD3170866-C664-4A42-A91D-49C9AF35AFCB_w1023_r1_s.jpg&h=708b906a&s={SIZE}\" />中國和菲律賓漁船同時出現在中國所稱的黃岩島附近有爭議海域（路透社2017年4月6日）"},{"pid":"02e3b36b3c9e240b5c7801b0b47b69276b1e1390","tid":2242785,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:22:31.000Z","msg":"打佢老母"},{"pid":"b84c92099f3bc025ba8bff13ee4f64365f8105c6","tid":2242785,"uid":264326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:24:23.000Z","msg":"請大家支持一下Uber 救護車同埋流亡手足<br />\n之前大家話門檻高<br />\n佢地提供左自由訂價眾籌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFacebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/119994513136471/posts/164908725311716/?vh=e&amp;extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F119994513136471%2Fposts%2F164908725311716%2F%3Fvh%3De%26extid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2gx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=2ab8ab3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/119994513136471/posts/164908725311716/?vh=e&amp;extid=0&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\nTg <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkuber/9344\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkuber%2F9344&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2gx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=645fe850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkuber/9344</a>"},{"pid":"2d80e0f5b637de62578570f6ce93f1fde4fd8264","tid":2242785,"uid":284245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}